comments: The single entered the German sales charts on 25.04.1994, reached No. 1 and dropped out end of September after 23 weeks. It also went top ten in Austria, Switzerland and other parts of Europe. The song was a radio hit in many countries and a huge dance hit in the summer holiday resorts. There are three mixes on this CD and further ones on other formats.
